{
  "texts": [
    "The usage of the metaverse may be seen as an enhancement of education through the employment of metaverserelated technologies that integrate components of real and virtual educational environments (Zhang et al., 2022).",
    "In fact, through the metaverse, students and instructors will be able to engage in the virtual world while simulating the social and emotional spheres of the real world.",
    "The use of the metaverse for educational goals will enable students to interact easily with one another, with the instructors, and with the environment (Dwivedi et al., 2022).",
    "It will allow students to access the educational environment through the use of wearable devices without being restricted by time or place, and it will enable them to utilize digital identities (e.g., avatars) to engage in a realtime manner.",
    "This in turn will increase collaboration in learning activities, although still making independent learning possible (Teng et al., 2022)."
  ]
}